{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000069", "chronotag": "1739874517238", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL69", "numeroOrdreDepot": "69", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0134", "triAmendement": "iaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabu", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA721896", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": "PA795998"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Faucillon et Mme&#160;K/Bidi"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 12", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 12", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 12", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0134.asp#D_Article_12"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Les auteurs de cet amendement proposent la suppression de la cr&#x00E9;ation d&#x2019;un d&#x00E9;lit &#x00AB;&nbsp;d&#x2019;incivilit&#x00E9; d&#x2019;habitude&nbsp;&#x00BB; qui &#x00E9;tend &#x00E0; l&#x2019;ensemble des infractions de nature contraventionnelle &#x00E0; la police du transport le r&#x00E9;gime p&#x00E9;nal existant en mati&#x00E8;re d&#x2019;infraction aux obligations tarifaires. Le fait de commettre une m&#x00EA;me infraction &#x00E0; cinq reprises serait d&#x00E9;lictualis&#x00E9;.</p><p>Ainsi, en punissant des m&#x00EA;mes peines (six mois d&#x2019;emprisonnement et 7 500 &#x20AC; d&#x2019;amende) des faits tr&#x00E8;s disparates et de gravit&#x00E9; variable (d&#x00E9;t&#x00E9;riorer des &#x00E9;tiquettes, mendier, cracher, uriner, vapoter, transporter une arme &#x00E0; feu, voyager sans titre de transport&#x2026;), ce dispositif contrevient au principe de proportionnalit&#x00E9; des peines en mati&#x00E8;re p&#x00E9;nale, qui pr&#x00E9;voit que le l&#x00E9;gislateur doit fixer une peine proportionnelle &#x00E0; la gravit&#x00E9; de l&#x2019;infraction et au degr&#x00E9; de responsabilit&#x00E9; de l&#x2019;auteur.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-22", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Non soutenu"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-27T16:47:25+01:00", "sort": "Non soutenu"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000069?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "74346", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}